<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to Slack [re]Minder <%= @user.name %></h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully configured your <em>Slack Minder</em> account</p>
    <p>Your email address (where Internet Calendar notifications will be sent) is <%= @user.email %>.</p>
    <p>All calendar events will be referenced to the <%= @user.tz %> TimeZone.</p>
    <hr />
    <p>You can change/update any of these by simply entering
      <pre>setup email: <%= @user.email %> timezone: <%= @user.tz %></pre></p>
    <p>Timezones are
      <ul>
        <li>1&nbs;-&nbsp;US Eastern</li>
        <li>2&nbs;-&nbsp;US Central</li>
        <li>3&nbs;-&nbsp;US Mountain</li>
        <li>4&nbs;-&nbsp;US Pacific</li>
        <li>5&nbs;-&nbsp;US Alaska/Hawaii</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <hr />
    <footer>&copy;2016, WebSembly, LLC</footer>
  </body>
</html>
